![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/72e820ec-e154-4f68-95c1-e86ab1a44335/Gj5NMTFWAAAgP9A.jpg)

Vic Joseph, Corey Graves & Booker T. Huffman welcomed the audience to the broadcast before transitioning into the opening match.

*   **NXT Women's North American Championship Match****: Stephanie Vaquer def. Fallon Henley (c) (w/ Jacy Jayne & Jasmyn Nyx) via Pinfall (Spiral Tap).**
    
*   **NXT Tag Team Championship Match: Fraxiom (Axiom & Nathan Frazer) def. Josh Briggs & Yoshiki Inamura via Pinfall (Catapulta Infernal on Inamura).**
    
*   After the match, a group of masked men (featuring Dion Lennox and former DPW World Champion Lucky Ali) attacked Briggs, Inamura & Fraxiom.
    
*   Stacks cut a promo from The D'Angelo restaurant, where he called out Shawn Spears for this Tuesday's NXT.
    
*   **Strap Match: Eddy Thorpe def. Trick Williams via Pinfall (Busaiku Knee).**
    
*   **Ethan Page def. Je'Von Evans via Pinfall (Twist of Fate).**
    
*   Stephanie Vaquer was interviewed by Sarah Schreiber, where she said she would keep an eye on the Main Event of the evening.
    
*   **NXT Championship - Triple Threat Match: Oba Femi (c) def. Grayson Waller & Austin Theory via Pinfall (Fall From Grace on Waller).**
    
*   Saquon Shugars, Dion Lennox, Osiris Griffin & Cutler James attacked Femi after the match.
    
*   Arianna Grace & Santino Marella met with Ava, saying they had things to talk about.
    
*   **NXT Women's Championship - Four Way Match:** **Giulia (c) def. Roxanne Perez, Bayley & Cora Jade via Pinfall (Northern Lights Bomb on Perez).**
    
*   Stephanie Vaquer appeared after the match. As the two champions held their titles high, Jordynne Grace appeared and confronted them. The three had a staredown to end the broadcast.